<C>__{paul}
<D>__{so, right here, by the x.}
<A>__{ted nods. paul signs. ted takes the envelope with the check, hands it to paul but doesn't let go. paul tries to pull it free. he looks at ted who looks right through him. just then, the lights go out. they're all in the dark.}
<C>__{paul }
<D>__{we, uh... avis? call municipal light and power and let them know i will... stop by in a bit.}
